Requirements
Python version >=3.7.3

Create a virtual environment to use it in a better way so that there won't be any conflict regarding versions of the library:
--Conda environment:
  conda create -n <name of your environment>
  conda activate <name of your environment>


--pip virtualenv:
  pip install virtualenv
  virtualenv <name of your environment>
  <name of your environment>\Scripts\activate

To install the libraries open the command line/ Terminal in the same directory and type:
pip install -r requirements.txt